---
/**
 * ZeroTrustChecklist.astro
 * Implementation checklist for zero trust adoption
 * Pure CSS, dark theme
 */
---

<div class="ztc-wrap">
  <h3 class="ztc-title">Zero Trust Implementation Checklist</h3>
  
  <div class="ztc-phases">
    <div class="ztc-phase" style="--i:0;">
      <div class="ztc-phase-header">
        <span class="ztc-phase-num">Phase 1</span>
        <span class="ztc-phase-name">Identity Foundation</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ztc-items">
        <div class="ztc-item">Enforce MFA on all accounts — no exceptions</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Implement SSO with conditional access policies</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Inventory all service accounts and API keys</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Deploy privileged access management (PAM)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="ztc-phase" style="--i:1;">
      <div class="ztc-phase-header">
        <span class="ztc-phase-num">Phase 2</span>
        <span class="ztc-phase-name">Network Segmentation</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ztc-items">
        <div class="ztc-item">Map all application communication flows</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Deploy micro-segmentation controls</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Replace VPN with identity-aware proxy</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Encrypt all internal traffic (mTLS)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="ztc-phase" style="--i:2;">
      <div class="ztc-phase-header">
        <span class="ztc-phase-num">Phase 3</span>
        <span class="ztc-phase-name">Continuous Verification</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ztc-items">
        <div class="ztc-item">Implement device health checks before access</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Deploy real-time risk scoring per request</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Automate access revocation on anomaly detection</div>
        <div class="ztc-item">Log everything — centralize in SIEM</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .ztc-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  .ztc-title {
    color: #f1f5f9;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .ztc-phases {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .ztc-phase {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: ztcFade 0.5s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: calc(var(--i) * 0.2s);
  }
  @keyframes ztcFade {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .ztc-phase-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .ztc-phase-num {
    background: #818cf8;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .ztc-phase-name {
    color: #f1f5f9;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .ztc-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .ztc-item {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ztc-item::before {
    content: '☐';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #4ade80;
  }
</style>
